_sText:
Ok, this is a second release of the map called GZ_Training. 

I did'nt want to delete the other version as I've found since they both run on our servers here in SA, Some prefer the new one and some don't. I Also Tried to see if I could eliminate CAMPERS :P 

Changes: Changed the map a little to try and make it more even for the CT's.
Cleaned it up a bit,  Since GZ_training was my 1st map, it really does look terrible in Hammer, So I decided to go over the whole map and clean it. No more Overlapping brush work etc etc 

Again thanks to all the tuts on FBSBANANA.
